title: Snoozed Folder
creator: vkjain
content: I have snoozed a few emails from the Gmail web client. These move into a separate folder called the snoozed folder. This folder is not visible or synced in the thunderbird client for android. Any way to sync and see this folder or get the mails from this folder? I tried searching under all mails and they did not show up.

title: Someone using my username/gmail
creator: fuzzythatsme.1
content: When I went to sign up for inbox home screen to my surprise I'm already signed in by someone else. They are using it with my Accounts.
